<p>Green Committee are committed to ensuring and encouraging that the College is a Green College.&nbsp; Being a Green College is one of our College values.&nbsp; From running awareness campaigns and sunflower growing competitions,&nbsp;to planning for a greener future of the College, Green Comm are an active presence in College life&nbsp;<a href="http://www.dur.ac.uk/butler.jcr/green">with their own page</a>&nbsp;featuring tips and suggestions.</p>